Class SpanningTreeTraceGenerator<T extends Event,U>

  • java.lang.Object

  • Type Parameters:

    public class SpanningTreeTraceGenerator<T extends Event,U>
extends CayleyGraphTraceGenerator<T,U>
    Trace generator that uses a spanning tree of the Cayley graph. This generator can achieve total coverage with respect to the equivalence class coverage metric, ce.
    Author:
    Sylvain Hall√©
